'''''Beneath the City Streets: A Private Inquiry into the Nuclear Preoccupations of Government''''' is a 1970 book by British author [[Peter Laurie (author)|Peter Laurie]]. It details the existence and necessity of [[underground bunker]]s, [[food depot]]s, and [[government safe haven]]s throughout underground [[London]].
