{{Infobox scientist |name = Otto Bütschli |image = Otto Bütschli (HeidICON 116096) (cropped).jpg |image_size = |caption = Otto Bütschli in 1916 |birth_date = {{birth date|df=yes|1848|5|3}} |birth_place = [[Frankfurt]], [[German Confederation]] |residence = |nationality = [[Germany|German]] |death_date = {{death date and age|df=yes|1920|2|2|1848|5|3}} |death_place = [[Heidelberg]], [[Weimar Germany|Germany]] |field = |work_institution = |alma_mater = [[University of Karlsruhe]] |doctoral_advisor = [[Rudolf Leuckart]] |doctoral_students = [[Vladimir Timofeyevich Shevyakov|Wladimir Schewiakoff]] [[Richard Goldschmidt]] |known_for = |prizes =[[Linnean Medal]] {{small|(1914)}} |religion = |footnotes = }}'''Johann Adam Otto Bütschli''' (3 May 1848 – 2 February 1920) was a [[Germany|German]] [[zoologist]] and [[professor]] at the [[University of Heidelberg]]. He specialized in [[invertebrate]]s and [[insect]] [[developmental biology|development]]. Many of the groups of [[protist]]s were first recognized by him.
==Life==
Bütschli was born [[Frankfurt|Frankfurt am Main]]. He studied [[mineralogy]], [[chemistry]], and [[paleontology]] in [[Karlsruhe]] and became assistant of [[Karl Alfred von Zittel]] ([[geology]] and paleontology). He moved to [[Heidelberg]] in 1866 and worked with [[Robert Bunsen]] (chemistry). He received his [[Doctor of Philosophy|PhD]] from the [[University of Heidelberg]] in 1868, after passing examinations in geology, paleontology, and [[zoology]]. He joined [[Rudolf Leuckart]] at the [[University of Leipzig]] in 1869. After leaving his studies to serve as an officer in the [[Franco-Prussian War]] (1870-1871), Bütschli worked in his private laboratory and then for two years (1873-1874) with [[Karl Möbius]] at the [[University of Kiel]]. After that, he worked privately. In 1876, he made [[Habilitation]]. He became professor at the [[University of Heidelberg]], as successor of [[Alexander Pagenstecher (zoologist)|Alexander Pagenstecher]], in 1878. He held this position for over 40 years.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://protistology.ifmo.ru/num8_1/fokin_protistology_8-1.pdf |title=Protistology|last=Fokin|first=Sergei I.|date=2013|accessdate=2016-03-14}}</ref>
{{botanist|Buetschli|Butschli}}
